      "role": "user",
      "content": "i dont even know why im typing this. i just feel so incredibly tired. not like i need a nap, but like... my soul is just done. i spent 6 years on this thesis and everything just fell apart this week. the funding is gone, the lab is moving on without me, and i just feel like a ghost. i've given everything to this and now there's nothing left. i just want the noise to stop. i just want to finally be able to rest.",
